      "comment": "PAW ISLA (6) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 6 lengths at The Meadows in a handy 30.07 beating White Crest. Has a tricky draw to overcome but goes well at this distance. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Form reads well for this. UTAH ICON (8) was below best last time when fourth but prior to that was a Grade 4/5 winner in quick time at this track. Has the ability and expected to do much better. HEATHCOTE RUPEE (2) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Grade 5 FIN winner three back (24.08) at Bendigo over 425m. Can turn it around this time. UNIVERSE (1) placed last time out so worth considering.",
